<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Page Not Found | Armila's Restaurant & Lounge</title>
<meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="assets/favicons/favicon-32x32.png">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --olive-deep: #4D5340; --olive-shadow: #2A2E22; --olive-black: #1A1D14;
  --saffron: #C8932F; --saffron-pale: #E8C97E;
  --terracotta: #D87545; --cream: #F5EFE0;
  --serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  --sans: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
}
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
body {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  background: var(--olive-shadow);
  color: var(--cream);
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 40px 20px;
  overflow: hidden;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 30%, rgba(200, 147, 47, 0.18) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 70%, rgba(216, 117, 69, 0.12) 0%, transparent 50%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
body::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='220' height='220' viewBox='0 0 220 220' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' stroke='%23DBB45C' stroke-width='0.6' opacity='0.4'%3E%3Cpath d='M110 30 L138 70 L182 70 L150 100 L162 144 L110 116 L58 144 L70 100 L38 70 L82 70 Z'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='110' cy='110' r='3' fill='%23DBB45C'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  background-size: 320px;
  opacity: 0.04;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.wrap {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  max-width: 640px;
  text-align: center;
}
.logo {
  width: 80px;
  margin: 0 auto 48px;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: rise 1000ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 200ms forwards;
}
.logo img { width: 100%; height: auto; }
.num {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(120px, 22vw, 220px);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 0.9;
  color: var(--saffron-pale);
  font-style: italic;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: rise 1100ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 400ms forwards;
}
h1 {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 52px);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  color: var(--cream);
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: rise 1100ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 600ms forwards;
}
h1 em { color: var(--terracotta); font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; }
p {
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: rgba(245, 239, 224, 0.75);
  max-width: 480px;
  margin: 0 auto 44px;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: rise 1100ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 800ms forwards;
}
.ctas {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: rise 1100ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 1000ms forwards;
}
.btn {
  padding: 16px 32px;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 400ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}
.btn-primary { background: var(--saffron); color: var(--olive-shadow); }
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--saffron-pale); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(200, 147, 47, 0.4); }
.btn-outline { background: transparent; color: var(--cream); border: 1px solid rgba(245, 239, 224, 0.4); }
.btn-outline:hover { background: var(--cream); color: var(--olive-shadow); border-color: var(--cream); }
@keyframes rise {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="logo"><img src="assets/logo-icon-transparent.png" alt="Armila's"></div>
    <div class="num">404</div>
    <h1>This dish isn't <em>on the menu.</em></h1>
    <p>The page you are looking for has moved or never existed. The kitchen, however, is still open.</p>
    <div class="ctas">
      <a href="index.html" class="btn btn-primary">Back to Home</a>
      <a href="menu.html" class="btn btn-outline">View the Menu</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
